<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=George_Orwell&action=edit&section=30.php.html" title="Edit section: Diaries">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Diaries">Diaries</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Orwell. <i>Diaries</i> by George Orwell, edited by Peter Davison (W.W. Norton &amp; Company; 2012) 597 pages; $39.95). Annotated edition of 11 diaries kept by the English writer, beginning in late August 1931 and ending in September 1949, a few months before his death.</li>
</ul>
